nodes.text: Docking bay TH X-11-38 was a starship docking bay that was located within New Tayana, a space city that orbited the planet Duros. During the Clone Wars, the bounty hunters Cad Bane, Dengar and Ttekket traveled to the city aboard a Personal Luxury Yacht 3000, and on arrival there they berthed their vessel in docking bay TH X-11-38.
Docking bay TH X-11-38 is one of many Star Wars Easter eggs named after George Lucas's first film, THX 1138.
